entry.para:
The benefits of a free-trade arrangement between AFTA and CER. There were three components to the study:
Consideration of how an AFTA-CER free-trade arrangement would fit in with existing arrangements for trade liberalisation in the region;
Quantitative analysis of the present structure of trade barriers by broad industry categories;
Economy-wide modelling of the introduction of an AFTA-CER trade and investment arrangement.
